The paper deals with the combination of online algorithms and machine learning, specifically in the context of the caching problem. This suggests that the paper is likely to be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information theory (cs.IT), or cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-categories.
